title: Stories PodChats: Disney Bracket 2
description:
Today we’re sharing an episode of Stories Podchats! This is the exciting conclusion of our Disney movie bracket. If you haven't had a chance to listen to the first one, go check it out. We already narrowed the field from 64 to 32. In this episode we'll be going through the rest of the matchups until we have a winner.

For more episodes of Stories Podchats, and for ad-free episodes, access to all of our ebooks, or to receive a thank you in a future episode, you can check us out on patreon.com/stories.
